  "content_id": "615da9fb-41b5-4cb8-8500-69e15ca3ce19",
  "description": "Reporting a person who cannot work with children or vulnerable adults",
  "details": {
    "body": "\n<div role=\"note\" aria-label=\"Information\" class=\"application-notice info-notice\">\n<p>Parents or members of the public who are concerned about someone working with children or vulnerable adults should contact the police, social services or the person’s employer.</p>\n</div>\n\n<h2 id=\"refer-someone-to-disclosure-and-barring-service-dbs\">Refer someone to Disclosure and Barring Service (<abbr title=\"Disclosure and Barring Service\">DBS</abbr>)</h2>\n\n<p>Employers must <a href=\"/government/publications/dbs-referrals-form-and-guidance\">refer someone to <abbr title=\"Disclosure and Barring Service\">DBS</abbr></a> if they:</p>\n\n<ul>\n  <li>sacked them because they harmed someone</li>\n  <li>sacked them or changed their role because they might have harmed someone</li>\n  <li>were planning to sack them for either of these reasons, but they resigned first</li>\n</ul>\n\n<div role=\"note\" aria-label=\"Warning\" class=\"application-notice help-notice\">\n<p>You’re breaking the law if you do not refer someone to DBS when you should.</p>\n</div>\n\n<p>Contact the helpline for help referring someone to <abbr title=\"Disclosure and Barring Service\">DBS</abbr>.</p>\n\n<div class=\"contact\">\n<p><strong>DBS helpline</strong> <br>\nTelephone: 0300 0200 190 <br>\n<a href=\"/call-charges\">Find out about call charges</a></p>\n</div>\n\n",
    "external_related_links": [

    ]
  },
